headline: Can Target’s Recent 6% Rally Signal a Turnaround for Investors in 2025?
summary: If you are trying to figure out whether to buy, sell, or just keep an eye on Target stock right now, you are definitely not alone. There has been plenty of action in the share price lately, and for investors, that means potential opportunity, as well as a good reason to analyze what is really going on beneath the surface. In the past week, Target has jumped 6.1%, and it is up 7.1% over the past month. Despite these short-term gains, though, Target’s longer-term performance tells a different...
